    </svg>`,
    title: 'Career DNA Profile',
    description: 'Your complete professional map — built through our conversations, not your typing. The foundation from which all documents and strategy are generated.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18.75a6 6 0 006-6v-1.5m-6 7.5a6 6 0 01-6-6v-1.5m6 7.5v3.75m-3.75 0h7.5M12 15.75a3 3 0 01-3-3V4.5a3 3 0 116 0v8.25a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
